"instead of duplicating such configuration across your controllers. For "
"example, you might want to enforce that all date fields are formatted a "
"certain way or that fields with a specific annotation are formatted in a "
"certain way. With a shared `FormatterRegistry`, you define these rules once, "
"and they are applied whenever formatting is needed."
